Achievements.Name: A FISTFUL OF STRAWBERRIES
Achievements.Description: You harvested your first strawberries, now a word of encouragement from our sponsor Somanto.

Achievements.Name: THE FIRST HEALING
Achievements.Description: The first planet nodule is healed.

Achievements.Name: TRIAL BY SPAWNER
Achievements.Description: You survived volcanoes, Spawners and dodged their offspring. Planet was right to chose you.

Achievements.Name: NO MORE BABY TALK
Achievements.Description: Planet is healing, now her cognitive abilities are re-emerging... pfuuu.

Achievements.Name: BASETOPIA
Achievements.Description: You deployed mobile power nodes. Now don't you go break our level designs.

Achievements.Name: FULLY OPERATIONAL
Achievements.Description: From itty bitty doggy robot, to rail upgraded mobile battle station, give us a roar.

Achievements.Name: CAPTURED MUTAGEL VAT
Achievements.Description: You guiltlessly destroyed the SOMANTO "Tower of Terror" and captured a Mutagel Vat.

Achievements.Name: HEALED THE PLANET
Achievements.Description: You have healed your planet and she is happy now. But for how long...

Achievements.Name: CAPTAIN PLANET
Achievements.Description: You have finished McDROID in normal. Do you want to try Challenge?

Achievements.Name: FIRST NIGHTMARE
Achievements.Description: You have achieved the impossible and won ONE nightmare level.

Achievements.Name: STRAWBERRY PIGGY
Achievements.Description: You farmed 1000 strawberries in one level of the campaign.

Achievements.Name: FIREFIGHTER
Achievements.Description: With ninja-skills you've flipped all your turrets out of harms way - in CHALLENGE.

Achievements.Name: TOUGHTANIUM UNDERPANTS
Achievements.Description: SOMANTO's anabolic seem to be working for you. You have finished the game in Challenge.

Achievements.Name: UZUMAKI DESKA ?
Achievements.Description: You survived The Spiral for 50 waves of vertigo inducing madness.

Achievements.Name: CHLOROPHYL ALLERGIES
Achievements.Description: Completed "Anti Bliss" without a single bliss engine or redwood.

Achievements.Name: ALL NIGHTMARE
Achievements.Description: The SOMANTO agents knocking at your door agree.

Achievements.Name: ANTI-SOMANTOISM
Achievements.Description: You have purchased no turret in Challenge mode.

Achievements.Name: FRIEND OF NIKOLA
Achievements.Description: You have completed a level buying and using only Tesla coils.
